Citation.sTitle: Volumetric Behavior and Saturated Pressure for Carbon Dioxide + Ethyl Acetate at a Temperature of 313.15 K
Citation.sAbstract: Volumetric property was measured for carbon dioxide + ethyl acetate at T = 313.15 K and pressures to 10 MPa. Saturated pressure was also measured by the synthetic method. The experimental data obtained were correlated with various equations of state.
